item.title: About
item.description: About the blog I anticipate this blog to be about most things data (data engineering, ML/AI, and software development) with a few sprinkles of lifestyle and personal topics that interest me. About Me Hello! I’m Brian Ha and the author of this personal blog. I am a data nerd who loves all things data and want to share my learning journey with like-minded people. I completed my undergraduate studies at Boston College (Go Eagles!
